					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">B1 is true. It all happens on a per-scanline basis, it doesn't matter where sprites start or end, every scanline the PPU scans all 64 sprites and picks the ones with the highest priorities for displaying.</div>

					<br clear="all" /><br />

